{"tid":309882,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（長文）上完人地個showroom，我決定辭職","createTime":"2017-07-05T11:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T03:29:13.000Z","uid":1189,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6800b8b88ace7f43acfca9c9be113bba8359cb","tid":309882,"uid":1189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"做緊sales要成日跑街，但每個月搵得萬幾。<br />\n咁岩之前有個客係女仔搵我，話佢岩岩轉工。<br />\n而家同幾個年輕創業家攪緊新野，<br />\n叫我上佢度睇下。<br />\n<br />\n上到去利園上面有個全層office，<br />\n原來佢地批發緊美國上市抗衰老產品同護膚品。<br />\n原來家下抗衰老係潮流，誠哥都要投廿十億。<br />\n佢地既產品有幾十位科學家研發，<br />\n當中有諾貝爾獎得主tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家佢地team leader已經搵緊幾十萬一個月。<br />\n雖然我唔知點搵錢，但跟個咁勁既人，<br />\n賣咁勁既brand一定好好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我聽日就辭職，跟佢地學野<br />\n賣呢個brand <br />\n<br />\nNu Skin !<br />\n<br />\n想像自己每個月搵十萬<br />\n日日開酒，船P，溝死女<br />\n<br />\n已經扯旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831a746c98a3e65c13098c6d7ec2cf6dcd2a0803","tid":309882,"uid":35071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"曲到直喎樓主"},{"pid":"4f5ccb35e32fe4a5bdeaf4478bb452b71af8ac4d","tid":309882,"uid":1189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曲到直喎樓主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩呀，大好機會黎呀<br />\n<br />\n我已經急不及待好想玩玩了"},{"pid":"4b53470e5f7a90331a868efcccfae6d7e1f7dd91","tid":309882,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"小小創意都冇"},{"pid":"0ddf677362ef432fc28c81d6037b80474977bf68","tid":309882,"uid":15237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"嘩 呢獲真係 fatfat 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02b174c9f